    "citation" : "Kaspari, S., P. Mayewski, S. Kang, S. Sneed, S. Hou, R. Hooke, K. Kreutz, D. Introne, M. Handley, K. Maasch, D. Qin, and J. Ren. 2007. Reduction in northward incursions of the South Asian monsoon since ~1400 AD inferred from a Mt. Everest ice core. Geophys. Res. Lett., 34, L16701, doi:10.1029/2007GL030440.",
    "type" : "publication",
